        <section class="section">
            <h2>Bag Buying Tips</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Think About Access</h3>
                    <p>Side access lets you grab your camera quickly. Back panel access is more secure but requires
                        setting the bag down.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Weather Protection</h3>
                    <p>Look for weatherproof zippers and included rain covers. Even "water resistant" bags need covers
                        in heavy rain.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="card">
                    <h3>Don't Look Like a Target</h3>
                    <p>Plain backpacks are less attractive to thieves than bags with obvious camera branding and tripod
                        holders.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
